{
  "stem": "20142.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And finally they told me where to go, what to do, and how to pick up the material, how to distribute.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this happened after they told me, we'll give you one dry run, testing me if I can really cope with the problem.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And as evidently I was very devoted, and I was trying very hard to pass the test.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And from that moment on, I knew that there is somebody who is always assisting me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I didn't know that it was a girl, or a boy, or a man, or whoever to overlook over my activities in distributing the leaflets.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The leaflets were wrapped around milk bottles and left at certain points for people to pick up.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was distributing these bottles on a-- on a bicycle, with a little [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] basket in front, from place to place.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And these bottles were wrapped in the news from the BBC.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was in a few areas, they would constantly change.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was one area around the very, very treacherous Marszalkowska Street.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You probably remember this street from-- Marszalkowska was the-- the street of marshals.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was named after the Marshal Pilsudski.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then there was one section, the other section was [INAUDIBLE], [INAUDIBLE] was very close to the Vistula River.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And if you knew the area, then you just know where to drop off the the bottles at what time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't know the people, I just knew where to drop it off.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The addresses.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They-- they were-- they were telling you from day to day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When you were picking up the bottles, then you were-- then you were told.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You had to learn how to remember addresses.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Without it, you could not exist.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You-- they would not give you any assignment.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
